    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me and is still in wonderful shape, ready for many more adventures! I\u2019ve taken care of it and it runs super smoothly, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'd love for you to come take a look and see how great it drives. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to help!",
