    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of BMW M engineering with this E92 M3, powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The engine's individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, and the dual-VANOS system ensures a broad power band up to the 8,400 RPM limit. The chassis dynamics are preserved through a well-maintained suspension setup and a communicative hydraulic steering rack. This example is in solid mechanical health with recent fluid service and throttle actuator inspection. While it displays minor cosmetic evidence of its journey, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain uncompromised, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
